{
  "id": "adv_event_2206_01_01",
  "title": "みんなで\n作る曲",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――I-UNITYセミファイナル数日前",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few days before the I-UNITY semi-finals",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 1.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "サニピの新曲と新衣装の制作が決まってすぐのこと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Soon after Sunny Peace's new song and outfits were decided to be produced",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.8,
      "endTime": 4.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "新曲と新衣装、制作の座組は整ったよ\nさっそく作業に入ってもらっている",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The new song and new outfits‚ the production team is ready.\nThey've already started working on it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5,
      "endTime": 10.934263038600001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_01-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます！\n急なお願いだったのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you very much!\nEven though it was a sudden request…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.1333333333,
      "endTime": 14.9346258004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことはないよ\nクリエイターさんもみんな乗り気だったし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's no big deal.\nThe creators were all enthusiastic too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.3666666667,
      "endTime": 19.6614984065,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "さくら達の熱意に触発されたみたいでな\n最高の曲を作ろうって言ってくれたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It seems like they were inspired by Sakura's passion.\nThey said they want to create the best song.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.8333333333,
      "endTime": 25.747369416599998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_01-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "心強いですね\n今から完成が楽しみです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's reassuring.\nI'm looking forward to the completion.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.0666666667,
      "endTime": 30.047097555799997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 30.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_01-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "それまでは私達も、セミファイナルに向けて\nしっかりレッスン重ねないと……だね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Until then‚ we need to focus on the semifinals.\nWe have to practice diligently…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.2333333333,
      "endTime": 37.803665516,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 38
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな、レッスンにはもちろん励んでもらうとして\n……実は、一つ提案がある",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ of course‚ I want you to work hard on rehearsals.\n…Actually‚ I have a suggestion.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38,
      "endTime": 44.833197403,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "みんなも、楽曲制作に加わらないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Would you all like to participate in the song production?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.3,
      "endTime": 48.300000047699996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_01-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "私達も……制作に？\n作曲とか、作詞とかを……ってこと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We… in the production?\nLike composing or writing lyrics…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.6,
      "endTime": 55.838843727000004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 56.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "さすがに作曲は全部プロに任せるけど\n作詞や振り付け、衣装デザインを手伝ってもらうんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Leave the composition entirely to the professionals‚ of course.\nBut I want you to help with the lyrics‚ choreography‚ and outfit design.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.0333333333,
      "endTime": 62.5452607473,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_01-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "振り付け……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Choreography…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.8333333333,
      "endTime": 64.46666666659999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_01-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "衣装デザイン……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Outfit design…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.7333333333,
      "endTime": 66.53333333329999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_01-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "確かに千紗ちゃんは\n以前、衣装デザインを手伝ったことがあったけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa-chan did help with\noutfit design before…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.8666666667,
      "endTime": 72.2250115077,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_01-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "あ、あれは、ちょっとアイデアを出しただけで\n私一人で出来た訳じゃないから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… I only came up with some ideas…\nIt wasn't something I did alone…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.5333333333,
      "endTime": 79.4421995481,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "今回も、基本的にはプロに任せる予定だ\nみんなには、ちょっとしたアイデア出しをお願いしたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This time‚ the professionals will be in charge‚ mainly.\nI just want everyone to contribute some ideas.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.7333333333,
      "endTime": 86.001791509,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 86.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_01-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "でも、私達は素人\n参加して邪魔にならないか、少し心配……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But we're amateurs for that…\nI'm a bit worried if our participation will be a hindrance…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.2333333333,
      "endTime": 94.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 94.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "雫の考えももっともだ。でも……\nこの話、提案してきたのは作曲家さん達なんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shizuku's concern is valid. But…\nIt was the composers who proposed this idea.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.9,
      "endTime": 102.3772789954,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 102.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_01-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "……え？　そうなんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Eh? Is that so?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.6333333333,
      "endTime": 105.1833333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。今回の制作は急ピッチで進められる\nだからこそ、制作段階から関わっておいた方がいい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. The production is progressing rapidly this time.\nThat's why it's better for you to be involved from the production stage.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.4,
      "endTime": 112.7999999047,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "そうして早いうちから曲への理解度を高めておけば\n少ない練習時間でも完成度を上げられる、ってね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By doing so‚ even with less practice time‚ .\nyou can raise the level of completion",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.1,
      "endTime": 120.0252832413,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_01-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "一理ありますね。ファイナルまで時間はない……\nそもそも、間にもう一戦、挟んでいる訳ですし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That makes sense. We don't have much time until the finals…\nBesides‚ we have another battle in between.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.3666666667,
      "endTime": 128.4508163135,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.3666666684
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 128.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "それに、練り上げていく段階でみんなが関われば\nサニピのエッセンスをより盛り込めるからって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Also‚ if everyone is involved in the development process‚\nWe can incorporate more of Sunny Peace's essence‚ they said.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.6666666667,
      "endTime": 134.7815870921,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 135.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
